{"tid":1874562,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"這個人值得歧視 - 李純恩","createTime":"2020-02-11T09:20:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-11T13:06:10.000Z","uid":25558,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"ad7044620aafda54866895b4b0af3c9c71e7c942","tid":1874562,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T09:20:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%B4%94%E6%81%A9/daily/article/20200210/20859261/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25B4%2594%25E6%2581%25A9%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200210%2F20859261%2F&d=e9hI6ag5UTzhCSVhase9yCrXKCTJ71YGEIw5q99tfRY%3D&h=791b7c2b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25B4%2594%25E6%2581%25A9%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200210%2F20859261%2F&h=30d2e306\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%B4%94%E6%81%A9/daily/article/20200210/20859261/</a><br />\n<br />\n這個人值得歧視 - 李純恩<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20200210/large/1581232680_be78.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20200210%2Flarge%2F1581232680_be78.jpg&h=ed023daa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nnow新聞截圖<br />\n<br />\n這天我說現在世衛的總幹事看起來髒兮兮的，朋友就說我種族歧視。我說這關種族歧視什麼事呢？一個人看起來乾淨還是髒，跟他的膚色沒有關係，長得再黑，像丹素華盛頓、摩根菲曼，你又何時覺得他們髒兮兮。<br />\n<br />\n但這個中文譯名叫譚德塞的世界衛生組織總幹事，一副樣子就不大乾淨，跟他頂着的那個衛生頭銜有感覺上的出入，不大衛生。<br />\n<br />\n這個看起來有欠衛生的世界衛生組織總幹事，銜頭不小，但水平卻不見得高，對於這次中國武漢肺炎的事態發展常常前言不對後語，如果你聽他第一次讚揚中國處理這次瘟疫如何成功的溢美之詞，就會覺得武漢官員說的「可控可防」也是實情了。要是你真的相信了他的話，全世界死的人大概要比現在多得多。他那種近乎馬屁的溢美之詞，大概連中國政府聽了都心虛，但這個世衛組織總幹事卻可以流暢說出來，可見不但沒水平，也沒人品。至於他說這種話有沒有臉紅，那倒是沒有看出來，因為他那張臉很難看出色澤變化。<br />\n<br />\n我的朋友聽我這麼說，大概又要怪我歧視人了，這點我也不否認了，我不會歧視種族，但一定會歧視人，若是一個人不像樣，長得多白我都歧視。這個世衛總幹事是值得歧視的，因為他看起來、聽起來都很不衛生，很靠不住。因此，也要順便讚一讚賜他中文名字的那個翻譯，「譚德塞」，「德」塞住了，便什麼都塞住了，由他領導世衛，世衛也靠不住了。這個翻譯朋友，還真有點先見之明。 <br />\n<br />\n李純恩<br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com"},{"pid":"10660d6fd89388dc5b1d2ebaba6d8800b9ddd4dd","tid":1874562,"uid":99568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T09:21:19.000Z","msg":"牙恩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d2e67a3af7717c8bb368ccec434e0c2a6c3e67d","tid":1874562,"uid":51625,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T09:22:09.000Z","msg":"條力架又係抵屌嘅"},{"pid":"0d84b30475d3fd3469e82e9e3a366ddc5726b6c8","tid":1874562,"uid":21545,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T09:22:52.000Z","msg":"直頭影衰黑人啦"},{"pid":"5c9fbd5b39fae5c50aebb7d27625077f5b915168","tid":1874562,"uid":220458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T09:23:04.000Z","msg":"佳文共賞"},{"pid":"f00f7a444851869bf5567c248cf1c05b1d5be187","tid":1874562,"uid":292585,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T09:23:06.000Z","msg":"李純恩都屌佢<br />\n條力架真係好撚摟屌"},{"pid":"415e94ceb853677f0dbf416713dc5cb544fa83f4","tid":1874562,"uid":181797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T09:24:29.000Z","msg":"奶共"},{"pid":"e689851b15b3f7e09a6c6ab368a26c54d1256748","tid":1874562,"uid":259319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T09:24:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ea35af660d0f5daf565d3ad64c6cd95d7913cb9","tid":1874562,"uid":77092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T09:24:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"183bd8bbfed7e1eee72d90fda069f533ec8a52dc","tid":1874562,"uid":293557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T09:26:32.000Z","msg":"係大陸撈都咁有勇氣踩WHO親中干部, 有膽識<br />\n<br />\n之前係一條上面見到佢開始畫野食, 意境高左好多<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/yitiaotv/posts/1264537707065314\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/l